    <item>
      <title>随着储户压力的增加，富国银行的NII下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/wells-fargo-sees-nii-drop-as-pressure-from-depositors-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行公司第一季度净利息收入未达到预期，这表明贷款增长放缓和支付更多存款的压力加大，正在侵蚀利率上升的好处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/wells-fargo-sees-nii-drop-as-pressure-from-depositors-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:01:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一位法国基金经理击败 97% 的同行，正在做空欧莱雅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/a-french-fund-manager-beating-97-of-peers-is-shorting-l-oreal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国化妆品巨头欧莱雅过去20年的年回报率接近12%，但卡米尼亚克多空欧洲股票投资组合经理马尔特·海宁格(Malte Heininger)现在开始做空该公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/a-french-fund-manager-beating-97-of-peers-is-shorting-l-oreal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:58:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于贷款令人失望，中国信贷扩张持续放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/china-s-credit-expansion-beats-expectations-in-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份中国信贷扩张继续放缓，银行发放的贷款少于预期，反映出由于央行没有放松货币政策，借贷需求仍然疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/china-s-credit-expansion-beats-expectations-in-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:55:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟贷款部门批准改革以增加国防资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/eu-s-lending-arm-to-approve-change-to-boost-defense-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲投资银行提出了一项计划，该计划将使国防项目的融资变得更加容易和快捷，以加强对欧洲安全和国防工业的支持。]]></description>
